WEBVTT

00:02:28.891 --> 00:02:30.269
na nikachagua mimi

00:02:32.446 --> 00:02:37.007
(Makofi)

00:02:38.673 --> 00:02:41.832
Mila ya familia yangu 
na matarajio ya mwanamke

00:02:41.856 --> 00:02:44.777
hayangeniruhusu nimiliki 
rununu mpaka kuolewa.

00:02:45.544 --> 00:02:47.627
Na ata nilpoolewa,

00:02:47.651 --> 00:02:51.738
kifaa hiki kikawa kifaa
cha ufuatiliaji wangu.

00:02:52.923 --> 00:02:57.353
Nilipokataa haya mafikira 
ya kufuatiliwa na mume wangu wa zamani,

00:02:57.377 --> 00:02:59.066
hakukubalina na wazo hilo

00:02:59.090 --> 00:03:01.174
na akanifurusha kutoka nyumbani,